what relationships and romance ought to be ... this version of jane austen 's persuasion is an excellent example of the subtlety and warmth that is missing from modern , so-called romances . anne and wentworth are the two sane people surrounded by a range of wacky characters trying to distract them from what 's really important . my husband and i are big fans of jane austen and this movie is one of our favorites , second only to the a & e five-hour version of pride and prejudice